PrecisORDER respecting the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL of CERTAIN LANDS in the YUKON TERRITORY (TR'ONDËK HWËCH'IN FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of certain lands in the Yukon in order to facilitate the settlement of Aboriginal land claims, and (b) the repeal of an earlier Withdrawal Order (P.C. 1997-1063).
